{
  "stem": "1895.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On August 16, they installed reflectors, so that they could work day and night in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And August 16, 17, and 18, in three days, working day and night, [SIGHS] they emptied the ghetto in Radom.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There must've been at least 23,000, 24,000 people there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, that was the group that my parents and sister were taken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was restricted to ammunition factory, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- night--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I worked nights, as I told you, and the factory machines would stop for lunch in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was in the summer time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was August, and the windows were open, so we clearly hear gunfire that was coming from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we looked at, and we could see, the lights, the reflectors, that they had put in, you know, to be able to work at night.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could see that from afar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like a glow of fire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I could barely function at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Out of the ghettos in Walowa and Glinice, which comprised over 35,000 Jews, after the resettlement action that took place on August 16, there were approximately 3,000 Jews left that were put into a two block area, which was called Targowiska, in one corner of the former ghetto.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was the end of the, you might say, of the Jewish community in Radom really.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those 3,000 were eventually shipped away as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a third deportation, which took place later on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But basically, they left the 3,000 people for a simple reason, that they needed workers--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To clean up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to clean up and process.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
